036-THE-BUSINESS-OF-LIFE?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1918\n| ''All Man''\n|Belle Foliot\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=All Man |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17013-ALL-MAN?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1918\n| ''Hoarded Assets''\n| Claire Dawson\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Hoarded Assets |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17129-HOARDED-ASSETS?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1918\n| ''Miss Ambition''\n| Edith Webster\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Miss Ambition |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/15078-MISS-AMBITION?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''[[The Undercurrent (1919 film)|The Undercurrent]]''\n| Mariska\n|[[Selznick Pictures|Select Pictures]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Undercurrent |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/15635-THE-UNDERCURRENT?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''Silent Strength''\n| Ruth Madison\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Silent Strength|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/15547-SILENT-STRENGTH?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''Beauty-Proof''\n| Carol Thorpe\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Beauty-Proof|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/15384-BEAUTY-PROOF?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''Beating the Odds''\n| Hebe Norse\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Beating the Odds|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17362-BEATING-THE-ODDS?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| '