-PROOF?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''Beating the Odds''\n| Hebe Norse\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Beating the Odds|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17362-BEATING-THE-ODDS?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''Fighting Destiny''\n| Caryl Rundlege\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Fighting Destiny|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17347-FIGHTING-DESTINY?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''[[The Man Who Won]]''\n| Barbara Le Moyne\n|Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Man Who Won|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17460-THE-MAN-WHO-WON?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1919\n| ''Dust of Desire''\n| Corrinne Torrence\n| Vitagraph\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Dust of Desire|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/15310-DUST-OF-DESIRE?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1920\n| ''[[Occasionally Yours]]''\n|Bunny Winston\n|[[L. J. Gasnier]] Productions\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Occasionally Yours|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/15985-OCCASIONALLY-YOURS?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1920\n| ''[[The Third Generation (1920 film)|The Third Generation]]''\n| Helen Van Dusen\n|Brentwood Film Corporation\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Third Generation|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/16164-THE-THIRD-GENERATION?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1920\n| ''[[The Silver Horde (1920 film)|The Silver Horde]]''\n| Mildred Wayland\n|Eminent Authors Pictures, Inc.\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The TSilver Horde|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17954-THE-SILVER-HORDE?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1920\n| ''[[Burnt Wings (1920 film)|Burnt Wings]]''\n| Helen\n|[[Universal Pictures|Universal Films]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Burnt Wings|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17667-BURNT-WINGS?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1920\n| ''[[Nomads of the North]]''\n| Nanette Roland\n|[[James Oliver Curwood]] Productions Inc.\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Nomads of the North|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/17837-NOMADS-OF-THE-NORTH?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1921\n| ''The Truant Husband''\n| Vera Delauney\n|Rockett Film Corp.\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Truant Husband|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/12863-THE-TRUANT-HUSBAND?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1921\n| ''Just Outside the Door''\n|Gloria Wheaton\n|Weber Productions\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Just Outside the Door|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/10047-JUST-OUTSIDE-THE-DOOR?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1921\n| ''[[The Queen of Sheba (1921 film)|The Queen of Sheba]]''\n| The Queen of Sheba\n|[[Fox Film]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Queen of Sheba |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/11493-THE-QUEEN-OF-SHEBA?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1921\n| ''[[Mother o' Mine]]''\n| Fan Baxter\n|[[Thomas H. Ince|Thomas H. Ince Productions]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Mother o' Mine |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/10863-MOTHER-O-MINE?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1921\n| ''[[Charge It]]''\n|Millie Garreth\n|Equity Pictures