. B. Productions\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Sinner or Saint |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/12154-SINNER-OR-SAINT?cxt=filmography|website=Silent Era : Progressive Silent Film List |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1923\n| ''[[The Darling of the Rich]]''\n| Charmion Winship\n|B. B. Productions\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Darling of the Rich |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/3633-THE-DARLING-OF-THE-RICH?cxt=filmography|website=Silent Era : Progressive Silent Film List |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n\n!scope=\"row\"|1924\n| ''[[Southern Love]]''\n| Dolores\n|Graham-Wilcox Productions\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=Southern Love (1924) |url=https://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b6b68f7d3 |website=BFI |accessdate=April 24, 2020 }}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1924\n| ''[[The Breath of Scandal]]''\n| Sybil Russell\n|[[B. P. Schulberg|B. P. Schulberg Productions]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Breath of Scandal |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/3019-THE-BREATH-OF-SCANDAL?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1924\n| ''[[The Spitfire (1924 film)|The Spitfire]]''\n| Jean Bronson\n| Murray W. Garsson Productions\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Spitfire |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/12354-THE-SPITFIRE?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1924\n|''[[The Recoil (1924 film)|The Recoil]]''\n| Norma Selbee\n|Goldwyn Pictures\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Recoil |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/11586-THE-RECOIL?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|1924\n|''[[The Folly of Vanity]]''\n| Mrs. Ridgeway\n|Fox Film\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=The Folly of Vanity |url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/9137-THE-FOLLY-OF-VANITY?cxt=filmography|website=catalog.afi.com |accessdate=Apr