e lion]]''' <br />''Panthera leo melanochaitus''\n|1876<br />\n|align=\"center\"|South Africa\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Rembrandt-A-Lion-Lying-Down-207063 detail.jpg|100px|Cape lion]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Cape serval]]''' <br />''Leptailurus serval serval''\n|Unknown<br />\n|align=\"center\"|South Africa\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Cape warthog]]''' <br />''Phacochoerus aethiopicus aethiopicus''\n|1871<br />\n|align=\"center\"|South Africa\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n\n|'''[[Kenya oribi]]''' <br />''Ourebia ourebi kenyae''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/15732/0 |title=''Ourebia ourebi ssp. kenyae (Kenya Oribi)'' |author=IUCN SSC Antelope Specialist Group |year=2008 |access-date=December 23, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref>\n|Unknown<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Kenya\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Large sloth lemur]]''' <br />''Palaeopropithecus'' sp.<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Hoffmann, M. | title = ''Palaeopropithecus ingens'' | volume = 2008 | page = e.T136532A4306543 | date = 2008 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2008.RLTS.T136532A4306543.en }}</ref>\n|data-sort-value=\"1550\" | 1500s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Madagascar\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Palaeopropithecus ingens.jpg|75px|Palaeopropithecus ingens]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Lesser Mascarene flying fox]]''' <br />''Pteropus subniger''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Mickleburgh, S. | author2 = Hutson, A.M. | author3 = Bergmans, W. | author4 = Howell, K. | last-author-amp = yes | title = ''Pteropus subniger'' | volume = 2008 | page = e.T18761A8580195 | date = 2008 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2008.RLTS.T18761A8580195.en }}</ref>\n|data-sort-value=\"1820\" | 1864-1873<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius and France (Reunion)\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Pteropus subniger.png|75px|Lesser Mascarene flying fox]]\n|-\n|'''[[Quagga]]''' <br /> ''Equus quagga quagga''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/7957/0 |title=''Equus quagga ssp. quagga (Quagga)'' |year=2008 |author=Hack, M.A. |author2=East, R. |author