ion kestrel]]''' <br />''Falco duboisi''\n|1700s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|France (Reunion)\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[R\u00e9union night-heron]]''' <br />''Nycticorax duboisi''\n|1700s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|France (Reunion)\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[R\u00e9union owl]]''' <br />''Mascarenotus grucheti''\n|1700s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|France (Reunion)\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[R\u00e9union pigeon]]''' <br />''Nesoenas duboisi''\n|1705<br />\n|align=\"center\"|France (Reunion)\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[R\u00e9union shelduck]]''' <br />''Mascarenachen kervazoi''\n|1690s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|France (Reunion)\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[R\u00e9union starling]]''' <br /> ''Fregilupus varius''\n|1850s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|France (R\u00e9union)\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Bourbon Crested Starling.jpg|75px|R\u00e9union starling]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Rodrigues night-heron]]''' <br /> ''Nycticorax megacephalus''\n|1750s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Rodrigues Night Heron.jpg|100px|Rodrigues night-heron]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Rodrigues owl]]''' <br />''Mascarenotus murivorus''\n|1750s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Rodrigues parrot]]''' <br /> ''Necropsittacus rodericanus''\n|1750s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Necropsittacus rodericanus.jpg|75px|Rodrigues parrot]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Rodrigues rail]]''' <br /> ''Erythromachus leguati''\n|1750s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Rodrigues Rail.png|100px|Rodrigues rail]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Rodrigues solitaire]]''' <br /> ''Pezophaps solitaria''\n|1778<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Pezophaps solitaria.png|75px|Rodrigues solitaire]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Rodrigues starling]]''' <br /> ''Necropsar rodericanus''\n|1750s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Rodrigues Starling.jpg|100px|Rodrigues starlingg]]\n|-\n|-\n|'