ani]]''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Reid, J.W. | title = ''Afrocyclops pauliani'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T611A13066717 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T611A13066717.en }}</ref> <br /> 1951, Madagascar\n* ''[[Namibcypris costata]]''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/611/0 |title=''Namibcypris costata'' |author=Inland Water Crustacean Specialist Group |year=1996 |access-date=December 27, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref> <br /> Unknown, Namibia\n* ''[[Tropodiaptomus ctenopus]]''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Reid, J.W. | title = ''Tropodiaptomus ctenopus'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T22379A9371437 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T22379A9371437.en }}</ref> <br /> Unknown, Madagascar\n\n== Molluscs ==\n\n* ''[[Caldwellia philyrina]]'' Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Campolaemus perexilis]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis blofeldi]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis exulatus]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis helena]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis melanoides]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis nonpareil]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis subplicatus]]''  Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis subtruncatus]]''  Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis turtoni]]''  Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Colparion madgei]]'' Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Ctenoglypta newtoni]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Cyclophorus horridulum]]'' Unknown, France (Mayotte)\n* ''[[Cyclosurus mariei]]'' Unknown, France (Mayotte)\n* ''[[Dupontia proletaria]]''  Unknown, France (Reunion) and Mauritius\n* ''[[Erepta nevilli]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gibbus lyonetianus]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gonidomus newtoni]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gonospira nevilli]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gulella mayottensis]]''  Unknown, France (Mayotte)\n* ''[[Har