Centre | author-link = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | title = ''Phelsuma gigas'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T16925A6598516 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T16925A6598516.en }}</ref>\n|1842<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Roque Chico de Salmor giant lizard]]''' <br />''Gallotia simonyi simonyi''\n|1930s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Spain (Canary Islands)\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Lacerta simonyi.jpg|100px|Roque Chico de Salmor giant lizard]]\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Round Island burrowing boa]]''' <br /> ''Bolyeria multocarinata''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Madagascar Reptile & Amphibian Specialist Group | title = ''Bolyeria multocarinata'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T2864A9488737 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T2864A9488737.en }}</ref>\n|1975<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Saddle-backed Mauritius giant tortoise]]''' <br />''Cylindraspis inepta''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | author-link = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | title = ''Cylindraspis inepta'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T6062A12385198 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T6062A12385198.en }}</ref>\n|data-sort-value=\"1720\" | Early 18th century<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Saddle-backed Rodrigues giant tortoise]]''' <br />''Cylindraspis vosmaeri''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | author-link = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | title = ''Cylindraspis vosmaeri'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T6065A12391587 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T6065A12391587.en }}</ref>\n|1800s<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Mauritius\n|align=\"center\"|[[File:Cylindraspis vosmaeri.jpg|100px|Saddle-backed Rodrigues giant tortoise]]\n|-\n|}\n\n== Amphibians ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"30%\" | Common name\\scientific name\n! width=\"15%\" data-sort-type=\"number\" | Extinction date\n! width=\"30%\" | Range\n! width=\"15%\" class=\"unsortable\" | Image\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Du Toit's torrent frog]]''' <br />''Arthroleptides dutoiti''\n|1962<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Kenya\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Osgood's Ethiopian toad]]''' <br />''Altiphrynoides osgoodi''\n|2003<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Ethiopia\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|'''[[Conraua derooi|Togo slippery frog]]''' <br />''Conraua derooi''\n|Unknown<br />\n|align=\"center\"|Ghana and Togo\n|align=\"center\"|--\n|-\n|-\n|}\n\n== Fish ==\n* ''[[Aplocheilichthys sp. nov. 'Naivasha']]''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/61225/0 |title=''Aplocheilichthys sp. nov. 'Naivasha''' |author=Hanssens, M. |year=2004 |access-date=December 28, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref> <br /> 1970s, Kenya\n* ''[[Barbus microbarbis]]''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/61247/0 |title=''Barbus microbarbis'' |author=Ntakimazi, G. |year=2006 |access-date=December 28, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref><br /> Unknown, Rwanda\n* ''[[Pantanodon madagascariensis]]''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/15949/0 |title=''Pantanodon madagascariensis'' |author=Loiselle, P. |author2=Participants of the CBSG/ANGAP CAMP \"Faune de Madagascar\" workshop |location=Mantasoa, Madagascar, 2001 |year=2004 |access-date=December 28, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref> <br /> Unknown, Madagascar\n* ''[[Ptychochromis onilahy]]''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/44504/0 |title=''Ptychochromis sp. nov. 'Kotro''' |author=Loiselle, P. |author2=Participants of the CBSG/ANGAP CAMP \"Faune de Madagascar\" workshop |last-author-amp=yes |location=Mantasoa, Madagascar, 2001 |year=2004 |access-date=December 28, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref> <br /> 1962, Madagascar\n* ''[[Salmo pallaryi]]''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Crivelli, A.J. | title = ''Salmo pallaryi'' | volume = 2006 | page = e.T61190A12440688 | date = 2006 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2006.RLTS.T61190A12440688.en }}</ref> <br /> 1930s, Morocco\n\n== Insects ==\n\n[[File:Labidura herculeana.jpg|thumb|right|50px|The [[Saint Helena earwig]]]]\n* ''[[Aplothorax burchelli]]'' <br /> Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Libythea cinyras]]''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | author-link = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | title = ''Libythea cinyras'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T11934A3316737 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T11934A3316737.en }}</ref> <br /> Unknown, Mauritius\n* [[Deloneura immaculata|Mbashe River buff]]<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | author-link = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | title = ''Deloneura immaculata'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T6331A12652621 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T6331A12652621.en }}</ref> <br /> ''Deloneura immaculata'', 1863, South Africa\n* [[Lepidochrysops hypopolia|Morant's blue]]<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | author-link = World Conservation Monitoring Centre | title = ''Lepidochrysops hypopolia'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T11537A3293608 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T11537A3293608.en }}</ref> <br /> ''Lepidochrysops hypopolia'', 1879, South Africa\n* [[Saint Helena giant earwig]]<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/11073/0 |title=''Labidura herculeana (Saint Helena Earwig, St Helena Earwig)'' |author=World Conservation Monitoring Centre |year=1996 |access-date=December 25, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref> <br /> ''Labidura herculeana'', 1967, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* [[Sympetrum dilatatum|Saint Helena darter]]<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Suhling, F. | author2 = Martens, A. | last-author-amp = yes | title = ''Sympetrum dilatatum'' | volume = 2011 | page = e.T21226A9259879 | date = 2011 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2011-1.RLTS.T21226A9259879.en }}</ref> <br /> ''Sympetrum dilatatum'', 1964, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n\n== Crustacean ==\n* ''[[Afrocyclops pauliani]]''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Reid, J.W. | title = ''Afrocyclops pauliani'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T611A13066717 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T611A13066717.en }}</ref> <br /> 1951, Madagascar\n* ''[[Namibcypris costata]]''<ref>{{cite iucn |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/611/0 |title=''Namibcypris costata'' |author=Inland Water Crustacean Specialist Group |year=1996 |access-date=December 27, 2013|ref=harv}}</ref> <br /> Unknown, Namibia\n* ''[[Tropodiaptomus ctenopus]]''<ref>{{Cite iucn | author = Reid, J.W. | title = ''Tropodiaptomus ctenopus'' | volume = 1996 | page = e.T22379A9371437 | date = 1996 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1996.RLTS.T22379A9371437.en }}</ref> <br /> Unknown, Madagascar\n\n== Molluscs ==\n\n* ''[[Caldwellia philyrina]]'' Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Campolaemus perexilis]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis blofeldi]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis exulatus]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis helena]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis melanoides]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis nonpareil]]'' Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis subplicatus]]''  Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis subtruncatus]]''  Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Chilonopsis turtoni]]''  Unknown, United Kingdom (Saint Helena)\n* ''[[Colparion madgei]]'' Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Ctenoglypta newtoni]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Cyclophorus horridulum]]'' Unknown, France (Mayotte)\n* ''[[Cyclosurus mariei]]'' Unknown, France (Mayotte)\n* ''[[Dupontia proletaria]]''  Unknown, France (Reunion) and Mauritius\n* ''[[Erepta nevilli]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gibbus lyonetianus]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gonidomus newtoni]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gonospira nevilli]]''  Unknown, Mauritius\n* ''[[Gulella mayottensis]]''  Unknown, France (Mayotte)\n* ''[[Harmogenanina 